1.0.name: wordpress/real-estate-mls-search
1.0.description:
Real Estate Cloud MLS IDX Search plugin allows you to publish MLS listings on your website and push the leads into Real Estate CRM available on our website.

Main Functionality:

*   MLS Search
*   Compliance (Login to see SOLD data, property description, etc)
*   Easy Install
*   Works on 95% of themes without any customization
*   SEO-friendly. Generates over 50 000 pages upon enabling
*   Allows customization of SEO tags on every page
*   Has calls to action, Facebook, Twitter, other SHARING functionality
*   Pushes leads into Real Estate CRM
